title: S4, Ep3: Lowkey Thankful
itunes:author: Loud Speakers Network
itunes:summary:
Things are getting messy and it’s spilling over into all aspects of Issa’s life. Crissle and Fran discuss awkward moments in public places, the telltale signs your friend is going to therapy and the downside to DIY.

Don’t forget to join in on the conversation and follow along on social media with the hashtag #insecuriTEA
